description:
Tap to Control Egg. Avoid hitting the pipes!

Collect the coins. But don’t you forget to look out for enemies and obstacles!

Fly Egg Fly is great for every age. Young and old can compete against each other. Families can enjoy lots of fun with this game. Just enjoy the flight around the field and collect all the coins. 5 Coins = 1 Point

√ Challenging achievements
√ Fun to play for everyone
√ Leaderboards

Fly Egg Fly is the BEST-looking FREE coin flappy bird game for your iOS Device!
